Token.Abstract: The RFC 5646 language code of the input text. If the request does not specify the language code, the service detects the dominant language. If you specify a language code that the service does not support, it returns UnsupportedLanguageException exception. For more information about RFC 5646, see Tags for Identifying Languages on the IETF Tools web site.
